        "creation_date": 1618165780,
        "body": "<p>You don\u2019t have to create a Chronicle queue per thread. You can create a single instance of Chronicle queue, then for each thread, create a tailer by calling createTailer. So it is only the tailer that you have to have per thread. Not the queue. Please try that and let me know if it helps.<\/p>\n",
